The SpeechSound is used to play randomised sounds directly from the .awc file. Typically used for, but not limited to, speech, ambience, pain and oneshot sounds.

Fields:

UnkInt0
UnkInt1
VoiceDataHash
SpeechName

Example:

  <Item type="SpeechSound">
   <Name>vb_female_01</Name>
   <Header>
    <Flags value="0x00000004" />
    <Unk02 value="65236" />
   </Header>
   <UnkInt0 value="1" />
   <UnkInt1 value="1" />
   <VoiceDataHash>vb_female_01</VoiceDataHash>
   <SpeechName>VB_ONESHOT</SpeechName>
  </Item>
